~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
~~ Meta Specific Configurations like setting VTank Options
STATE: {Setup} ~~ {
	IF:	Always
		DO:	DoAll				
				DoExpr {$questFlag=`tormentshardpickup`}
				DoExpr {$questName=`Curator of Torment`}
				SetOpt {EnableNav} {true}
				SetOpt {EnableLooting} {false}
				SetOpt {EnableCombat} {true}
				Return
~~ }

STATE: {Death} ~~ {
	IF: Always
		DO: DoAll
				SetOpt {EnableNav} {true}
				Return
~~ }

